comment_data.body:
`VV_ARGF` only contains the file arguments (from global_alist),  not the full command line. ex_restart needs to rebuild the complete  v:argv including all flags, so VV_ARGF is not applicable here. main function of 35889
 
```C
static void set_argf_var(void)
{
  list_T *list = tv_list_alloc(kListLenMayKnow);

  for (int i = 0; i < GARGCOUNT; i++) {
    char *fname = alist_name(&GARGLIST[i]);Expand commentComment on line R1511Resolved
    if (fname != NULL) {
      (void)vim_FullName(fname, NameBuff, sizeof(NameBuff), false);
      tv_list_append_string(list, NameBuff, -1);
    }
  }

  tv_list_set_lock(list, VAR_FIXED);
  set_vim_var_list(VV_ARGF, list);
}
```

